## RESPONSIVE DESIGN BREAKPOINTS

```css
/* Mobile First Approach */

/* Base styles (mobile - 320px+) */
body {
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.container {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 12px;
  max-width: 100%;
}

.card {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.buttons {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
}

/* Tablet optimization (768px+) */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .card {
    display: inline-block;
    width: calc(50% - 6px);
  }

  .card:nth-child(odd) {
    margin-right: 12px;
  }

  .sidebar {
    display: block;
    width: 250px;
    float: left;
  }

  .main-content {
    margin-left: 250px;
  }
}

/* Desktop optimization (1025px+) */
@media (min-width: 1025px) {
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
  }

  .card {
    display: inline-block;
    width: calc(33.333% - 8px);
  }

  .modal {
    max-width: 600px;
    position: fixed;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }
}
```

