## PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATION

### 1. IMAGE OPTIMIZATION

**Problem:** Large images slow down mobile loading  
**Solution:** Responsive images

```html
<!-- Responsive images with srcset -->
<img 
  src="doctor-small.jpg"
  srcset="
    doctor-small.jpg 320w,
    doctor-medium.jpg 768w,
    doctor-large.jpg 1200w"
  sizes="(max-width: 320px) 300px,
         (max-width: 768px) 700px,
         1100px"
  alt="Doctor photo"
/>

<!-- Picture element for different formats -->
<picture>
  <source srcset="doctor.webp" type="image/webp" />
  <source srcset="doctor.jpg" type="image/jpeg" />
  <img src="doctor.jpg" alt="Doctor" />
</picture>
```

**CSS optimization:**
```css
img {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}

/* Lazy loading images */
img[loading="lazy"] {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f0f0f0 25%, #e0e0e0 50%, #f0f0f0 75%);
  background-size: 200% 100%;
  animation: loading 1.5s infinite;
}

@keyframes loading {
  0% { background-position: 200% 0; }
  100% { background-position: -200% 0; }
}
```

### 2. CSS OPTIMIZATION

**Use CSS instead of JavaScript:**
```css
/* Good - CSS only */
.button-pressed {
  background-color: var(--btn-active-color);
  transform: scale(0.98);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

/* Avoid - JavaScript animation */
/* element.style.backgroundColor = ... */ /* Bad */
```

**CSS variables for themes:**
```css
/* Define once */
:root {
  --primary-color: #2180CE;
  --primary-dark: #1a66a0;
  --primary-light: #3391e8;
  --btn-height: 48px;
  --btn-radius: 4px;
  --spacing-sm: 8px;
  --spacing-md: 16px;
  --spacing-lg: 24px;
}

/* Use everywhere */
.btn {
  height: var(--btn-height);
  background-color: var(--primary-color);
  border-radius: var(--btn-radius);
}

/* Dark mode override */
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --primary-color: #64b5f6;
    --primary-dark: #42a5f5;
  }
}
```

### 3. JAVASCRIPT OPTIMIZATION

**Debounce expensive operations:**
```javascript
function debounce(func, wait) {
  let timeout;
  return function executedFunction(...args) {
    const later = () => {
      clearTimeout(timeout);
      func(...args);
    };
    clearTimeout(timeout);
    timeout = setTimeout(later, wait);
  };
}

// Usage
const handleSearch = debounce(performSearch, 300);
searchInput.addEventListener('input', handleSearch);
```

**Lazy load modules:**
```javascript
const modules = {};

async function loadModule(name) {
  if (!modules[name]) {
    const module = await import(`./modules/${name}/${name}.js`);
    modules[name] = module;
  }
  return modules[name];
}

// Only load when needed
navigation.addEventListener('click', async (e) => {
  const moduleName = e.target.dataset.module;
  await loadModule(moduleName);
});
```

### 4. NETWORK OPTIMIZATION

**Compress data:**
```javascript
// Only send necessary fields
const appointmentData = {
  id: appointment.id,
  patientName: appointment.patientName,
  doctorId: appointment.doctorId,
  date: appointment.date,
  time: appointment.time
};

fetch('/api/appointments', {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
  body: JSON.stringify(appointmentData)
});
```

